Package: WALS
Title: WALS - Weighted Average Least Squares
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Kevin",
           family = "Huynh",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "kevin.huynh@unibas.ch",
           comment = c(""))
Description: Implements the Weighted Average Least Squares (WALS) method 
	for negative binomial regression of Huynh (2023), for linear regression models 
	(Magnus et al., 2011) <doi:10.1016/j.jeconom.2009.07.004> and 
	generalized linear models (De Luca et al., 2018) <doi:10.1016/j.jeconom.2017.12.007>. 
	WALS for the linear regression model is based on the original MATLAB code by 
	J.R. Magnus and G. De Luca <https://www.janmagnus.nl/items/WALS.pdf>, 
	see also <doi:10.1007/s13571-013-0060-9>, <doi:10.1111/joes.12094> and 	
	<doi:10.1177/1536867X1201100402>. 
URL: https://github.com/kevhuy/WALS
License: GPL-2 | GPL-3
